  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of CJ-12420 in Patients With Erosive Esophagitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Dose-finding Study to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of CJ-12420 in Patients With Erosive Esophagitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
